Set of converters for conversion of one systems biology format into an other.

Class Summary
BioPAXToCytoscapeConverter Converts BioPAX (represented by BioPAX object) to XGMML (represented by GraphDocument object)
BioPAXToCytoscapeConverter.Graph Little auxillary container for BioPAX and GraphDocument object
BioPAXToCytoscapeConverter.Option Set of conversion options
BioPAXToSBMLConverter Converts BioPAX (represented by BioPAX object) to SBML (represented by org.sbml.x2001.ns.celldesigner.SbmlDocument object)
CellDesignerColorSpecies  
CellDesignerToBioPAXConverter Implementation of converter from CellDesigner 3.* file to BioPAX
CellDesignerToCytoscapeConverter Direct converter from CellDesigner to Cytoscape.
CellDesignerToCytoscapeConverter.Graph Simple container for GraphDocument and SbmlDocument objects
CytoscapeToBioPAXConverter Deprecated class.
CytoscapeToCellDesignerConverter Class used to export a part of CellDesigner file, using only species and reactions visualized in the current Cytoscape network
parseBioPAX Utility class for listing some BioPAX information as a readable text
parseCellDesigner Utility class for listing some CellDesigner information as a readable text
